               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <subc>III,3</subc> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> colludere </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> invicem sese oblectare </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> ludere </t:quote></cit> re, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> tempus fallere </t:quote></cit> [i.q. <foreign xml:lang="ar">لَهَا</foreign> VI] (in libris mss. saepius <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተለሀየ፡</foreign> scriptum reperitur, pro <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተላሀየ፡</foreign>; <lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> <bibl><ptr target="bm:Dillmann1857Gramm"/></bibl> § 48,4): <foreign xml:lang="gez">እስመ፡ ዮጊ፡ ይትላሀይ፡</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="grc">ὅτι ἀδολεσχία αὐτῷ ἐστιν</foreign> 3 <ref cRef="Reg." loc="18,27">Reg. 18,27</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወአኀዝኩ፡ አነሂ፡ እትላሀይ፡ ምስሌሆን፡</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang="grc">παίζειν μετ᾽ αυτῶν</foreign>) <ref cRef="Herm." loc="86">Herm. 86</ref>; (infans arcam farinariam in manus sumsit) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ከመ፡ ዘይትላሀይ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Gad. T.H." loc="">Gad. T.H. </ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">እመ፡ ፈቀድነ፡ ንትላሀይ፡ ንሕሊ፡ ማሕሌተ፡ መንፈሳዊተ፡</foreign> F.M. 32,7; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኦድንግል፡ አኮ፡ በተላህዮ፡ ዘልህቂ፡ ከመ፡ አዋልደ፡ ዕብራውያን፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Lit." loc="171,1">Lit. 171,1</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጽብቱ፡ ምስሌሁ፡ ወተላህዩ፡ ነዋኀ፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> longe natando certate cum eo! </t:quote></cit> <ref cRef="Jsp." loc="323">Jsp. 323</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተላሀይክሙ፡ በነፍሳቲክሙ፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> in aleam dedistis vitam </t:quote></cit> <ref cRef="Jsp." loc="361">Jsp. 361</ref>; de <foreign xml:lang="grc">μετεωρισμοῖς τῆς θαλάσσης</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="gez">መንክር፡ ተላህያ፡</foreign> (var. <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተልህያ፡</foreign>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለባሕር፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Ps." loc="92,6">Ps. 92,6</ref>; repetitum in Lit. Epiph. Dicitur de variis ludis: de ludis athletarum: <foreign xml:lang="gez">እለ፡ ይትላሀዩ፡ ወይዛበጡ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Chrys. Ta." loc="19">Chrys. Ta. 19</ref>; ludere calculis et latrunculis: (sacerdotes) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢይትላሀዩ፡ ግብረ፡ ሰንጠረጅ፡ ወገበጣ፡ ወኢይበጽሑ፡ ኀበ፡ መካን፡ ዘይትላሀዩ፡ ቦቱ፡</foreign>F.M. 32,7; instrumentis musicis: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተላህዮሰ፡ እንተ፡ ይእቲ፡ ተላህዮ፡ በዕፅ፡</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang="ar">العُود</foreign>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወዕንዚራ፡ ወአርጋኖን፡ ወተረፈ፡ ንዋያተ፡ ማሕሌት፡ ዘተውኔት፡ ሕሩም፡ ውእቱ፡</foreign> F.M. 32,7. Deinde in legibus canonicis saepius de manustupratione Sodomitarum libidinibus usurpatur: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለእመ፡ ተላሀየ፡ ካህን፡ በነፍስተ፡ ሥጋሁ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Kedr f." loc="67">Kedr f. 67</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ለእመ፡ ተረክበት፡ ብእሲት፡ ምስለ፡ ካልእታ፡ ይትላሀያ፡ በበይናቲሆን፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Kedr f." loc="63">Kedr f. 63</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዝሙት፡ ወተላህዮት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Gad. Ad." loc="149">Gad. Ad. 149</ref>. – <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> Voc. Ae. </t:quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ተዛውዐ፡ ተላሀየ፡ ዘ፡ ተጫወተ፡</foreign> </sense>
               
            
